OL,3,CLockers, hot-desks and buddy-system:
OL,4,CHow MPs spend their first day in
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FMonday is the start of the first full
OL,8,Fweek in office for MPs, with new-
OL,9,Fstarters and veterans alike making
OL,10,Ftheir journeys from across the UK to
OL,11,FWestminster to settle into their roles.
OL,13,FOut of the 650 MPs elected at last
OL,14,Fweek's General Election, 335 have
OL,15,Fnever held office before.
OL,17,FThe start of any job is typically
OL,18,Ffilled with a day or two of admin and
OL,19,Flogistics, and Parliament is no
OL,20,Fdifferent.
