OL,3,CLockers, hot-desks and buddy-system:
OL,4,CHow MPs spend their first day in
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FUpon their arrival at the Commons, a
OL,8,Fwelcome pack is issued to each MP
OL,9,Fcontaining key resources, information
OL,10,Fand guidance to help them start their
OL,11,Fnew jobs at Parliament.
OL,13,FThey will also be given a key,
OL,14,Fattached to a coloured tag, to their
OL,15,Fown locker.
