OL,3,CLockers, hot-desks and buddy-system:
OL,4,CHow MPs spend their first day in
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FEventually all MPs will have their own
OL,8,Foffice, but in the meantime, hot-
OL,9,Fdesking spaces and lockers are
OL,10,Fprovided so they "can start helping
OL,11,Ftheir constituents immediately,"
OL,12,Faccording to Parliament.
OL,14,FOn their first day, every MP will be
OL,15,Fpaired up with a "buddy," who will not
OL,16,Fhave a political affiliation and will
OL,17,Fbe available to help brief them on
OL,18,Ftheir role, to help them navigate the
OL,19,Festate and give advice on
OL,20,Fparliamentary procedure and etiquette.
