OL,3,CLockers, hot-desks and buddy-system:
OL,4,CHow MPs spend their first day in
OL,5,CParliament
OL,7,FThe parliamentary year will formally
OL,8,Fstart following the State Opening of
OL,9,FParliament, which will be held on July
OL,10,F17.
OL,12,FThe King's Speech at the State Opening
OL,13,Fwill set out the government's proposed
OL,14,Fpolicies and legislation for the
OL,15,Fcoming session.
